The download site: http://www.backmes.de/scripts+programs/randomsig.el

Configuration:

Place randomsig.el into your load-path and put the following in your .emacs file:

 (require 'randomsig)

(Re-)Start your emacs and type

 M-x customize-group RET
 randomsig RET

to customize the randomsig package.
----
